  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1673499">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1673499/" class="title-link">《群己论识》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1673499"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuezhixianzhe/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1566359-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuezhixianzhe/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月之仙者</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-10"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-10 23:46:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1673499_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      再过几个小时就得离开家了，在睡觉前我终于把看了将近半个月的书看完了。这本书是北大政管院的李强老师去年1月出版的《群己论识》，因为主要是作者的一些随笔、讲座之类，所以并不难读，之所以看的这么慢，主要是因为自己太过懒散，这段时间一直静不下心来。早上五点就得起...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1673499/#comments">(2回应)</a>
